Is it hard to support an artist who does multiple things? 
I never gave this thought before but it’s been brought to my attention a lot last few years. The idea is “I need to focus on one thing to not confuse people”. And to make sure my time and attention isn’t split. I see truth in that. I also feel like “fuck all that. Just make dope Shit”.

Rap is a contact sport for me. They can keep all that fake shit over there !!

@kvnallnphotography <<<
Designed by @deezusssss

Yo I am so excited to announce, we did it! We’ve officially sold out of the 25 limited edition preorders of my debut photography book, Everything Has A Place. 25 books locked down in 24 hours. 

My DMs have been blowing up with people who didn’t get theirs yet, and really wanna cop this book, and support the kid. So we’ve decided to open the limited edition window, so you can grab yours. 

But don’t worry, my first 25ers, we got somethin special for you. For holdin it down we’ll be gifting you with a special photo print along with your book order. It’s really no way we’d be here without you.

Friday, June 9th we’re hosting a Preorder Party at @kinfolxoak where we’ll be opening the floor for conversation about the book with @OGPenn from @KQED. Pull up to celebrate with us and get a little taste of what you’ll find in Everything Has a Place.

For context purposes. 
“Franklin Saint”  from the album Nothing Lasts Forever

Some of my favorite shots from the Mt Westmoore show 2022. I really got to take pics of my hero’s. 🙏🏾

Thank you to everyone who showed up. Stepping into new ventures may seem natural for me, but it’s all new and equally scary when you’re putting yourself on display. I think it’s easy to assume I have it figured out the whole time I’m just guessing and trying to be as honest with who I am internally all while being true to the art. Badu said it best…
I’m appreciative of everyone who’s given me  space to bounce ideas and helped me with creative solutions putting this book together. @_bakari thank you bro. Keep connecting these dots. @deezusssss it’s not possible without your eye for design and patience with my process 🙏🏾 
S/O @snapcollectiveworld for pushing the button and getting this done. @kinfolxoak & @ogpenn y’all came through and executed a plan in no time. Much love. 

Hopefully this is only the beginning. “Everything has a place” available for pre-orders now.

Happy bday @manidraper 
I’m not gone write you no love letter on here. 😂 but Foreal. One of one. Even though you’re from the southside, I still love you bro. let’s get this billion real quick.

Big love to everyone who already preordered their book. We’ve got 24 more hours left on our Presales for the book, so if you haven’t gotten yours yet please go on head and go for it. Once the presale is over you won’t be able to find this book anywhere else. Hit that link in our bio. 

And another thank you to @_bakari and @ogpenn @deezusssss @snapcollectiveworld for making all this a possibility. Wouldn’t be here without y’all’s help.

Happy Father’s Day Pop. Thank you for giving me the freedom of choice, for giving  me space to be a kid, and for being supportive when i said “I don’t wanna go to college. I wanna make art”. Thank you.
